International authors represented in the collection include: Breyten Breytenbach;
                Ahmet Hamdi Tanpinar; Francis Ponge; Julio Cortázar; Tadeusz Rozewicz; Marguerite
                Duras; Robert Musil; Henri Michaux; Elias Khoury; João Cabral de Melo Neto; Witold
                Gombrowicz; and Jean Giono. Translators represented include: Michael Henry Heim;
                Richard Sieburth; Richard Zenith; Lee Fahenstock; Bill Johnston; Peter Wortsman;
                Daniel Slager; Robert Bonono; and Peter Theroux.
